name: geopandas
raw_recipe:
{% set version = "0.2.1" %}

package:
    name: geopandas
    version: {{ version }}

source:
    fn: geopandas-{{ version }}.tar.gz
    url: https://github.com/geopandas/geopandas/archive/v{{ version }}.tar.gz
    sha256: 1e1845acbf6cf8dd2850aec9bfaa92892e462887903e3ea1abb8111e88a41206

build:
    number: 0
    script: python setup.py install --single-version-externally-managed --record record.txt

requirements:
    build:
        - python
        - setuptools
        - cython
    run:
        - python
        - pandas
        - pyproj
        - shapely
        - fiona
        - gdal 2.1.*
        - six
        - rtree
        - descartes
        - matplotlib
        - psycopg2  # [not win]
        - sqlalchemy
        - geopy ==1.10.0
        - pysal

test:
    imports:
        - geopandas
        - geopandas.io
    files:
        - test_data/test.cpg
        - test_data/test.dbf
        - test_data/test.shp
        - test_data/test.shx
    commands:
        - conda inspect linkages -n _test geopandas  # [not win]

about:
    home: http://geopandas.org
    license: BSD 3-clause
    summary: 'Geographic pandas extensions.'

extra:
    recipe-maintainers:
        - ocefpaf
        - jorisvandenbossche
